      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄭風·008.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">女曰鷄鳴.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>弋言加之，與子宜之。宜言飲酒，與子偕老。琴瑟在御，莫不靜好。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When your arrows and line have found them,
I will dress them fitly for you.
When they are dressed, we will drink together over them,
And I will hope to grow old with you.
Your lute in your hands,
Will emits its quiet pleasant tones.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-008__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879-fulltext">
